<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.6">
<l>ceppā ṭuṭaiya tirumā lavaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">centā maraikkai viralain tiṉaiyuṅ</l>
<l>kappā kamaṭut tumaṇi neṭuntōḷ</l>
<l rend="indent">kāmpā kakoṭut tukavit tamalai</l>
<l>yeppā ṭumparan tiḻiteḷ ḷaruvi</l>
<l rend="indent">yilaṅku maṇimut tuvaṭam piṟaḻak</l>
<l>kuppā yameṉa niṉṟukāṭ citaruṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that Tirumāl, possessed of righteousness,</l>
<l>[used to] cover [the cowherds],</l>
<l rend="indent">holding [it] with all five fingers of his red lotus hand</l>
<l rend="indent">as the spokes,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and his] long sapphire [hued] arm as the shaft,</l>
<l>called Govardana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where clear waterfalls descend, spreading everywhere,</l>
<l rend="indent">appear as if as a coat of shining strings of jewels</l>
<l rend="indent">and glittering pearls,</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
